comp3111.coursescraper

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • comp3111.coursescraper.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    A course can be identified by a unique course code. COMP3111 and COMP3111H are two different courses althought they are co-listed. It records title,description, exclusion, slots, number of slots, whether it is a common core and the enrollment status.
